data.description: THIS is the home you have been waiting for in Potranco Acres! The best priced home per square foot in this neighborhood! Why wait for a home to be built when you can move in to this beautiful, almost new, home right away! Gorgeous! Complete with high end finishes throughout, including Michael Edwards cabinets, Quartz countertops, oversized wood grain tile floors, coffered ceiling detail in office and dining room, beautiful custom lighting throughout! Window coverings already in place and stay with the house. This welcoming open floorplan is perfect for gatherings and entertaining or just hanging out. Enjoy the openness of the Texas sized kitchen, dining and living room. Be glorified by the stone fireplace that touches the cathedral ceiling, making it your statement piece! Bring your big screen TV to mount above the rough sawn mantle waiting for your decor.  Already wired for surround sound, ready for your entertainment system! Extra large, king sized bedrooms each come with en-suite bathrooms. The primary bedroom has a huge bathroom with a luxurious soaking tub and a magnificent, unique rotunda shower! The large walk in closet conveniently leads to the oversized laundry room. And let's not forget to mention there is a large office and ALSO a den/game/movie/flex room!       As you step out back you will enjoy the huge covered back patio (also pre-wired for surround sound) with a fireplace, your private backyard that is cleared and waiting for your vision and creativity. Get your hot tub ready because this home is ready and wired for one! While you're tubbing you can also enjoy the peace and quiet of this private, ONE ACRE greenbelt lot (Lot measurements: 175.98' x 249.98')  You'll see and hear the wildlife in this small gated community of only 93 homes.   The 3 car attached garage allows ample space for your vehicles and even has a mini split to keep them comfy!       Besides being a gated community you'll have added security with the local fire department and police sub station just outside the gate. Along with the home's Simplysafe Security System which stays with the house.       Come and tour this home, fall in love, make an offer!
